                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(center)\">\n                                        <placeName>New York</placeName>\n                                        <date>Shebat 17<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi> 5609</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>\n                                        <addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                                        <placeName>Philada</placeName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Dear Sir</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(3)\">In answer to yours I have to communicate<lb/> that\n                                        I have another <add>ספר תורה</add> on hand entirely new\n                                        and<lb/> most Splendid written I may say better than the\n                                        former<lb/> you have seen at the same amount $75 or $70. I\n                                        have<lb/> also a new <add>מגילה</add> in fact various, from\n                                        16 to 12, if you<lb/> know of Any <add>קהילה</add> in want\n                                        of the above named articles<lb/> please to name the parties\n                                        or “<add>שלוחו של אחד כמותו</add>”</p>\n                              <p>The subject of which I wanted to meet you, is<lb/> that “<add>כבוד\n                                                  ה הסתר המזל</add>” <persName>Mr Isidore\n                                                  Bush</persName> from\n                                                  <placeName><sic>Wienna</sic></placeName> is<lb/>\n                                        residing here in town and calling on me, as having<lb/> debt\n                                        with him and having confidence in me, his idea<lb/> being to\n                                        commence or rather resume his printing estab-<lb/>lishment\n                                        here, having a large apartment of Hebr. &amp; Germ.<lb/>\n                                        types on hand, there are more particulars concerned\n                                        which<lb/> I cannot mention here, if you might think\n                                        proper<lb/> that anything can or could be done with us it\n                                        would<lb/> to my opinions create much good to all parties,\n                                        and<lb/> would perhaps induce the American Israelites to\n                                        procure<lb/> to their families many books, not possessing at present.<lb/>\n                                        <persName>Mr. I B</persName>; having means to undertake the\n                                        creation of<lb/> a new Establishment, and I would be\n                                        selected<lb/> by him as his <add>בא עזר</add> and salesman\n                                        here ect.<lb/> “please to consider about it” most Respy\n                                        Yours</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(6)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">Simon <add>?</add></persName>\n                              </p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3599zj2s/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
